 top in the ring destroyed his life outside of it.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":4.6734,"vote_count":4664,"poster_path":"/1WV7WlTS8LI1L5NkCgjWT9GSW3O.jpg","release_date":"1980-11-14","vote_average":7.908,"backdrop_path":"/tvNuhRlpRozDgsX1zR9gQ2aHv1X.jpg","original_title":"Raging Bull","original_language":"en"},{"id":1632,"adult":false,"title":"Mississippi Burning","video":false,"overview":"Two FBI agents investigating the murder of civil rights workers during the 60s seek to breach the conspiracy of silence in a small Southern town where segregation divides black and white. The younger agent trained in FBI school runs up against the small town ways of his partner, a former sheriff.","genre_ids":[18,80,9648,53],"popularity":2.2884,"vote_count":1879,"poster_path":"/wvEx2WbxZXYljQ9vSoq37NgeXcJ.jpg","release_date":"1988-12-08","vote_average":7.679,"backdrop_path":"/sYpNbnOlIKW5nlrPDFOGpnCUlz9.jpg","original_title":"Mississippi Burning","original_language":"en"},{"id":273404,"adult":false,"title":"I'll Follow You Down","video":false,"overview":"After the disappearance of a young scientist on a business trip, his son and wife struggle to cope, only to make a bizarre discovery years later - one that may bring him home.","genre_ids":[878,18,9648],"popularity":0.7079,"vote_count":190,"poster_path":"/3osrKXIz5OkSrpnEt1hqHAAyvbd.jpg","release_date":"2013-07-28","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/hBaZ0cXy2gOwOvsywez8MHWgAjO.jpg","original_title":"I'll Follow You Down","original_language":"en"},{"id":1857,"adult":false,"title":"The Transformers: The Movie","video":false,"overview":"The Autobots must stop a colossal planet-consuming robot who goes after the Autobot Matrix of Leadership. At the same time, they must defend themselves against an all-out attack from the Decepticons.","genre_ids":[16,878,28,12,10751],"popularity":2.5696,"vote_count":580,"poster_path":"/xJ5W0mOAWCVaXmU0pBZh4NjSRv2.jpg","release_date":"1986-08-08","vote_average":7.128,"backdrop_path":"/8NvaYUSmpe56dBz7